HEADWORD: Decreasing
<hw>De*creas"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Becoming less and less;
diminishing.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>De*creas"ing*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Decreasing series</b></col> <fld>(Math.)</fld>, <cd>a
series in which each term is numerically smaller than the preceding
term.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Decreation</ent>⟦br⟧
